 * • Background: Near-black (#071226) for contrast
 * • Text: Pure white (#F8FAFC)
 * • Glows are visible and prominent
 * • Additive blending creates light effects
 * 
 * Light Mode is the "professional" aesthetic:
 * • Primary color: #2F4ED8 (deeper blue)
 * • Secondary: #4F6BFF (lighter blue)
 * • Background: Off-white (#FAFBFD)
 * • Text: Dark slate (#0F172A)
 * • Glows are subtle (normal blending)
 * • Paper-like appearance
 * 
 * Both modes share:
 * • Same typography (IBM Plex Sans)
 * • Same component structure
 * • Same animations (just different intensities)
 * • Consistent academic feel
 */

/**
 * MOBILE OPTIMIZATIONS (< 768px)
 * 
 * HomepageScene:
 * • Reduced particle count (1200 vs 2500)
 * • No floating constellation nodes
 * • No grid plane (performance)
 * • Still shows animated wordmark and starfield
 * • Uses 1x DPR instead of 1.5x
 * 
 * AttendanceRing3D:
 * • Falls back to SVG entirely
 * • No Canvas rendering
 * • SVG circle with animation
 * • Same visual effect, better performance
 * • Touch-friendly
 * 
 * Rationale: Mobile devices have limited GPU memory.
 * SVG is more efficient than WebGL for simple shapes.
 */

